<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 09:12:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>与共和党争斗后，拜登签署乌克兰援助计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/after-battle-with-republicans-biden-sign-ukraine-aid-package-2024-04-24/</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登将于周三签署一项法案，为乌克兰与俄罗斯的战争提供数十亿美元的新援助，这是总统在寻求连任之际取得的两党胜利，并为那些指望华盛顿提供帮助的盟友们带来鼓舞。支持基辅。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 09:04:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/after-battle-with-republicans-biden-sign-ukraine-aid-package-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>德国极右翼政治家誓言在助手被指控为中国从事间谍活动后不会辞职</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/german-far-right-politician-vows-not-quit-after-aide-accused-spying-china-2024-04-24/</link><description>德国极右翼德国选择党(AfD)欧洲议会一名成员周三表示，在一名助手因涉嫌为中国从事间谍活动而被捕后，他不会辞职。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 08:57:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/german-far-right-politician-vows-not-quit-after-aide-accused-spying-china-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>印尼央行称中国支付宝+尚未申请许可</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/indonesia-cenbank-says-chinas-alipay-yet-request-permit-2024-04-24/</link><description>印尼央行副行长 Filianingsih Hendarta 在周三的新闻发布会上表示，中国蚂蚁集团旗下支付宝+尚未正式申请在印尼开展业务的许可。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 08:29:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/indonesia-cenbank-says-chinas-alipay-yet-request-permit-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>台湾对美国援助计划感到满意，中国反对出售武器</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-happy-with-us-aid-package-china-objects-arms-sales-2024-04-24/</link><description>台湾总统蔡英文周三表示，她很高兴美国国会通过了一项全面的对外援助计划，其中包括对台湾的武器支持，而中国则敦促华盛顿停止向台北出售武器。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 06:28:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-happy-with-us-aid-package-china-objects-arms-sales-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>随着中欧紧张局势加剧，Polestar可能利用美国工厂向欧洲销售汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/polestar-may-use-us-plant-sell-cars-europe-eu-china-tension-rises-2024-04-24/</link><description>中国支持的瑞典电动汽车 (EV) 制造商 Polestar Automotive 首席执行官表示，鉴于地缘政治紧张局势加剧，该公司正准备将其计划销往欧洲的汽车生产从中国转移到美国工厂。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 06:02:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/polestar-may-use-us-plant-sell-cars-europe-eu-china-tension-rises-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>碧桂园获准推迟三只境内债券的首次付款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/chinas-country-garden-extends-bonds-avoid-first-local-default-bloomberg-news-2024-04-24/</link><description>陷入困境的中国房地产开发商碧桂园表示，已获得债券持有人批准，将三只境内债券的付款进一步推迟至9月，以便有更多时间筹集资金。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 05:57:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/chinas-country-garden-extends-bonds-avoid-first-local-default-bloomberg-news-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国的电动汽车生存游戏带来危险和力量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-ev-survival-game-creates-peril-power-2024-04-24/</link><description>从大多数标准来看，中国最不需要的就是更多的电动汽车挤入一个输家多于赢家的市场，以牺牲利润为代价压低价格，并争夺中国以外的市场份额。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 05:45:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-ev-survival-game-creates-peril-power-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>美国寻求对币安创始人赵判处 36 个月监禁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-seeks-36-months-jail-binance-founder-zhao-2024-04-24/</link><description>美国检察官周二在一份法庭文件中表示，全球最大的加密货币交易所币安创始人赵长鹏在承认违反反洗钱法后，应入狱 36 个月。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 05:44:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-seeks-36-months-jail-binance-founder-zhao-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>Orsted表示，为台积电提供电力的台湾风电项目有望于2025年完成</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/orsted-says-taiwan-wind-project-power-tsmc-track-2025-finish-2024-04-24/</link><description>全球最大的海上风电场开发商丹麦Orsted周三表示，台湾的一个项目将为芯片制造商台积电提供电力，进展顺利，有望于明年完工。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 05:26:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/orsted-says-taiwan-wind-project-power-tsmc-track-2025-finish-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>沃尔沃汽车第一季度销量增加，今年需求旺盛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-q1-adjusted-operating-earnings-rise-costs-ease-2024-04-24/</link><description>瑞典汽车制造商沃尔沃汽车周三表示，在第一季度销量增长后，预计今年汽车需求良好，但由于 Polestar 业务收入下降和亏损，营业利润未达预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 05:08:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-q1-adjusted-operating-earnings-rise-costs-ease-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>布林肯开始访华后，美中关系有所改善，但分歧仍很严重</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/better-us-china-ties-still-deep-disagreements-blinken-starts-visit-2024-04-24/</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周三抵达上海，美中关系基础更加稳定，但一系列令人畏惧的悬而未决的问题威胁着全球竞争对手之间关系的稳定。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 05:04:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/better-us-china-ties-still-deep-disagreements-blinken-starts-visit-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟对中国医疗器械市场启动调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-opens-investigation-into-chinese-medical-device-market-2024-04-24/</link><description>欧盟委员会周三对中国公共采购医疗器械展开调查，这是试图保护欧盟生产商免受其所说的不公平竞争影响的最新举措。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 05:01:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-opens-investigation-into-chinese-medical-device-market-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国华为推出新的智能驾驶软件品牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-huawei-launches-new-software-intelligent-driving-2024-04-24/</link><description>中国科技公司华为（HWT.UL）周三推出了一个新的智能驾驶软件品牌，标志着其为成为电动汽车行业主要参与者而做出的最新努力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 03:57:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-huawei-launches-new-software-intelligent-driving-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市因科技股上涨而上涨；干预观察中日元脆弱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-24/</link><description>亚洲股市周三在科技股的带动下大幅上涨，因本周投资者的注意力转向美国科技领头羊的财报，而日元仍深陷 34 年来的低点附近，令交易员对日本当局的干预保持警惕。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 03:06:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉在中国推出 Model 3、Model Y 零首付</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-offers-zero-down-payments-model-3-model-y-china-2024-04-24/</link><description>特斯拉社交媒体账户上的一则通知显示，特斯拉公司已为其在中国的 Model 3 和 Model Y 车辆提供零首付。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 02:14:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-offers-zero-down-payments-model-3-model-y-china-2024-04-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>